315
00:20:54,700 --> 00:20:56,569
Mustahil memeriksa semuanya.

316
00:20:56,770 --> 00:20:57,940
Ada sebanyak itu?

317
00:20:58,440 --> 00:21:00,409
Hei. Itu lucu.

318
00:21:00,409 --> 00:21:02,409
- Ada mobil kami juga.
- Sungguh?

319
00:21:02,879 --> 00:21:05,210
Ada yang mengendarai Starex semalam?

320
00:21:05,550 --> 00:21:07,780
